            <li><h2 class="mb-3 text-[#CB2026] font-bold text-xl">Phase 3: The Packaging Evolution</h2>
                The birth of <strong>RADIANCE BLOSSOM</strong> wasn't solely about its formulation. Embracing our ethos of environmental stewardship, our packaging design took shape. Every detail meticulously considered - sustainable materials, intuitive usability, and a visual testament to our reverence for the planet.</li>
                <li><h2 class="mb-3 text-[#CB2026] font-bold text-xl">Phase 4: A Sustainable Legacy</h2>
                    With every batch produced, our commitment to sustainability shines brighter. From responsible sourcing to eco-friendly manufacturing, <strong>RADIANCE BLOSSOM</strong> isn't just a product; it's a testament to our unwavering pledge to leave a greener footprint on this Earth.</li>
